  Resources.resw
  Windows App SDK Package Resource Index source file for StarStrike string resources.
  Compiled to resources.pri by makepri.exe at build time.

  Keys match the string identifiers in StarStrike/Text.cpp (asFixedID[]).
  All values are the English (en-US) localised strings sourced from
  GameData/messages/strings/Strings.txt.

  Additional string files that must be migrated to separate .resw files:
    - GenStrings.txt     -> GenStrings.resw
    - ResStrings.txt     -> ResStrings.resw
    - Cam1Strings.txt    -> Cam1Strings.resw
    - Cam2Strings.txt    -> Cam2Strings.resw
    - Cam3Strings.txt    -> Cam3Strings.resw
    - TutStrings.txt     -> TutStrings.resw
    - Names.txt          -> Names.resw
    - ScrStrings.txt     -> ScrStrings.resw
  Place each file alongside this file so makepri.exe picks them all up.
-->
